    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Young Women's Christian as\nISOLATION is making plans to secure\nlarger quarters. 1t aims to enlarge\nthe work and the present quarters\nin the Van Valkenburg block on Riv-\nerside are not adequate.\n\n\nWhen larger quarters are secured\n1t is proposed to furnish working\ngirls substantial lunch and a home\nlike place to spend the noon hour.\nThis will be done at a price just\nsufficient to cover the cost of carry\ning on the good work.\n\n\nAt present tea is served to girls\nwho go to the rooms Of the associa-\nton with their lunches."
    }
  ]
